.... The Predator is the 1911 John Browning would have loved to have made. By eliminating the barrel bushing and installing a full-length guide rod and a coned (wafered) match grade barrel, accuracy is improved and recoil is reduced. The Predator is the perfect candidate for protection, uniform, competition, hunting and recreational employment. Mr. Browning would be envious.
